    {
        "url": "/quotes/said_nursi_680952",
        "quote": "The fact that there is a unity in everything demonstrates that they are the works and artefacts of a single being. The universe is like a rosebud swathed in a thousand veils of unity. Or it is a single macroanthropos dressed in unities to the number of Divine Names and universal Divine works.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Said Nursi",
            "url": "/quotes/said_nursi_680952"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Like",
